That and myself, of course.
00:01:53.670 --> 00:01:54.540
Of course.
00:01:54.540 --> 00:01:56.310
So, right, what about animals?
00:01:56.310 --> 00:02:05.080
Well, it's interesting, right, but not a lot of folks realize that we're 90% of the same as a fly or a cockroach or a pigeon.
00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:09.250
That's the new science out there that's called genistics, I think.
00:02:09.250 --> 00:02:13.840
Which is going to be real popular real soon.
